<br>
needs:<br>
53+ person, preferably caster<br>
Corpses, all consented to the 53+<br>
<br>
the player gets consent, binds in prep room.<br>
<br>
Jumping down into the pits, the person drags corpses into vox's lair and gets banished....once banished, gate back and repeat. When all of the corpses get close to exit, monk or SK will pull the corpses to prep room. =)<br>
<br>
just some interesting info i thought might be useful for next time<br>
